metadata.name: Sunset at the East River
metadata.description:
Portfolio: One Photo A Day...
Street Series - New York City
Project Phase - Phase I (Nov. 1, 2022 ~ Oct. 31, 2023)

I grew up in the city and have lived in major cities such as Tokyo, Paris and New York City throughout my life. Paving the streets and documenting movement of people, building and atmosphere via photography give me a purpose in life. The One Photo A Day... portfolio project is one that I started on November 1st, 2022. Phase I of the project is 365 days. Only selected curated photos from the project will be minted as NFTs.
